quotes: "I love Valentine's Day and came across a really cute sloth decoration not long ago. It just fit."

label: Briscoe Door 2

label: Goodbody Door 1
description: Dorm door with stickers saying STEM and a whole wreath
quotes: "Our dorm is decorated with flyers from each of the events that the Women in STEM LLC has hosted. They are a colorful reminder of the events that have brought our community together, and they represent the memories we've formed over the course of this year."
